00:15:23.489 --> 00:15:29.379
Now please, take down your both the hands
and open your eyes slowly, very slowly.

00:15:30.436 --> 00:15:41.856
Now watch Me without thinking - you can do
it. Now, put up your right hand like this

00:15:42.305 --> 00:15:48.375
and bend your head and see for yourself,
if there's a cool breeze coming out of

00:15:48.375 --> 00:15:59.778
your head. Bend your head. It is above your
head, not on, so little away from the head

00:15:59.778 --> 00:16:06.333
you try to feel, if there's a cool breeze
coming out of your head. You can take

00:16:06.333 --> 00:16:14.270
your hand little further. Some people have
it quite away from the head, so see for

00:16:14.270 --> 00:16:25.099
yourself there's a cool breeze coming in.
Now, put the left hand towards Me and

00:16:25.099 --> 00:16:33.808
put down your head. Now see for yourself,
again with the right hand, if there's a

00:16:33.808 --> 00:16:37.807
cool breeze coming out of your head. Some
people will get heat coming out, doesn't

00:16:37.807 --> 00:16:43.226
matter, it will later on be followed by
a cool breeze also. To see yourself, if

00:16:43.226 --> 00:16:48.350
there is a cool breeze coming, bend your
head properly - that's important. Now,

00:16:49.499 --> 00:16:54.509
again put your right hand towards Me
and bend your head. Now, don't doubt.

00:16:54.787 --> 00:16:59.837
The breeze is coming from inside and not
from the air conditioner, so see for yourself.

00:17:00.283 --> 00:17:06.013
Again, this is the cool breeze of the Holy
Ghost; Is Kundalini is the Holy Ghost. Now see.

00:17:17.856 --> 00:17:27.496
Now, raise your both the hands towards the
sky, push back your head and here you ask

00:17:27.496 --> 00:17:34.503
a question, "Mother, is this the cool breeze
of the Holy Ghost?" "Mother, is this the

00:17:34.503 --> 00:17:39.899
All-Pervading Power of Divine Love?"
"Mother, is this the Param Chaitanya?"

00:17:39.899 --> 00:17:47.127
Ask any one of this question, three times.
Push back your head fully and ask this question.

00:17:53.365 --> 00:18:00.855
Separate your hands, don't put them together.
Separate your hands. May God bless you!

00:18:00.915 --> 00:18:09.703
Bring down your hands, please. Can watch 
Me without thinking. See. Now those, who

00:18:09.703 --> 00:18:16.951
have felt the cool breeze or even a hot breeze
out of their heads or on their finger-tips,

00:18:17.184 --> 00:18:30.102
please raise both your hands. The whole of
Sydney is drowned into the ocean of joy.

00:18:30.102 --> 00:18:41.897
May God bless you! So, the Kundalini has
sprouted, Kundalini has come out, you are

00:18:41.897 --> 00:18:48.474
connected with that but you have to
establish yourself otherwise it would be

00:18:48.474 --> 00:18:53.749
like the marshy land, where
Christ has described,

00:18:53.749 --> 00:18:58.146
"Some seeds fell down, they sprouted
and were destroyed."
